name: AWSConfigDeliveryChannelConfigSnapshotDeliveryProperties
description: ConfigSnapshotDeliveryProperties is a property of the AWS::Config::DeliveryChannel resource that specifies how AWS Config delivers configuration snapshots to the S3 bucket in your delivery channel.

properties.name: DeliveryFrequency
properties.description: The frequency with which AWS Config delivers configuration snapshots. For valid values, see ConfigSnapshotDeliveryProperties in the AWS Config API Reference.
